Scenario: Perform XmlSerializerTest
Given an XmlSerializer for SampleModel
When asked to marshall object to XML:
|stringElem|intElem|
|sample|1111|
Then xml should be:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?>
<Sample>
	<StringElem>sample</StringElem>
	<IntElem>1111</IntElem>
</Sample>
When asked to marshall null SampleModel
Then xml should be:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?>
<Sample>
	<IntElem>0</IntElem>
</Sample>
When asked to unmarshall XML to object:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?>
<Sample>
	<StringElem>sample</StringElem>
	<IntElem>1111</IntElem>
</Sample>
Then object should be:
|stringElem|intElem|
|sample|1111|
When asked to unmarshall empty XML
Then object should be null